The paper proposes a game-theoretical mechanism design for incentivizing smartphone users to provide sensing services in a mobile crowdsensing system. This involves designing a reverse auction mechanism to recruit participants with uncertain mobility. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.GT (Game Theory and Decision Science), followed by cs.MA (Multiagent Systems), cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture), cs.SI (Social and Information Networks), and cs.CY (Computers and Society).
